    "Metadata": {
        "Title": "The Shopkeeper-Eraser-Tron!",
        "Description": "Oh hello, Agent Perry! I can only assume that you are here to stop from activating my latest invention.\r\rTake a look at the Shopkeeper- Eraser-Tron! have you ever took a trip in a market? These places are filled to the grim with greedy and scammy shopkeepers who only hunt you for you to buy their overpriced merch.\r\rI. Am. Sick of it! I&#39;m getting rid of them all, and you can not do anything about it. Let&#39;s have fun!\r\rThis contract was created by a member of the HITMAN community known as Switcher.",
